    <div class="qa">
      <div class="question">Difference between slice and splice</div>
      <pre><code>slice()  -> Copies array without changing original.
splice() -> Changes original array.</code></pre>
    </div>

    <div class="qa">
      <div class="question">Difference between map, filter, reduce</div>
      <pre><code>map()    -> Transforms elements.
